# Component Development

## True Native Architecture

Components are built for **build-time platform separation**:
- `*.web.ts` - Web implementation
- `*.ios.swift` - iOS implementation  
- `*.android.kt` - Android implementation

No runtime platform detection - each platform gets its own native implementation.

## Token-First Approach

1. **Always** use design tokens over hard-coded values
2. Use semantic tokens first, primitives only when no semantic exists
3. Reference tokens by name: `icon.size100` not `24px`

